Summary: Unofficial Tapo API Client. Works with TP-Link Tapo smart devices. Tested with light bulbs (L510, L520, L530, L535, L610, L630), plugs (P100, P105, P110, P115), power strips (P300, P304), hubs (H100), switches (S200B) and sensors (KE100, T100, T110, T300, T310, T315).
